<span class="header1">Chat Activity</span>
		  
          <p class="arabic_lg"><strong><span class="arabic_lg">أنا اسمي ... ما اسمك؟ </strong></p>
          <p align="left">You are an exchange student in Cairo studying Arabic. During the orientation gathering you will be meeting the other students in your program. Prepare five questions in Arabic about things that you would like to ask about your classmates as well as five responses that will help you introduce yourself to them when you log on for the chat. Include the following information in your questions and potential responses: </p>
          <p>Name <span class="arabic_lg">الإسم</span></p>
          <p>Nationality<span class="arabic_lg"> الجنسيّة </span></p>
          <p>Occupation<span class="arabic_lg"> العمل </span></p>
          <p>The name of the university that you attend<span class="arabic_lg"> الجامعة </span></p>
          <p>Your residence (include, city and area)<span class="arabic_lg"> السكن، المدينة، المنطقة </span></p>
          <p>&nbsp; </p>
          <p>Note: Refer to the <a href="ps_1.html">Personalized Practice section</a> of Chapter 1 for further practice with this activity prior to the chat. </p>
          

